---
---

<section class="exec-section exec-section-auto exec-agentic" id="exec-agents">
  <div class="agentic-bg">
    <img src="/branding-identity/backgrounds/particle-field.png" alt="" class="agentic-bg-img" />
    <div class="agentic-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="exec-inner agentic-content">
    <div class="exec-label">The Killer Feature</div>
    <div class="exec-big">Meet your <em class="hl-gold">agentic workforce.</em> They never call in sick. They never drop a task. And they get smarter every week.</div>
    <p class="agent-intro-text">This is not a chatbot. This is not an automation script. Machina deploys <strong>autonomous AI agents</strong> that work alongside your human team, each specialized for a different operational function. They observe, learn, execute, and escalate, operating across your workflows, queues, communications, and patient records 24 hours a day.</p>

    <div class="agent-cards">
      <!-- Communications Agent -->
      <div class="agent-card exec-reveal">
        <div class="agent-card-header">
          <div class="agent-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="agent-label-text">Communications Agent</div>
            <div class="agent-name">Omni-Channel Routing</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-desc">Handles inbound and outbound patient communications across SMS, telephony, and video. Routes to the right team member when human judgment is needed. Follows up autonomously when it is not.</div>
        <div class="agent-impact">
          <div class="agent-impact-label">Why Your COO Cares</div>
          <div class="agent-impact-text">Patient touchpoint coverage goes from <strong>68%</strong> to <strong>99.2%</strong>. Every missed call that used to mean a lost patient is now an agent-handled interaction. Revenue leakage from communication failures drops to near zero.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Queue Agent -->
      <div class="agent-card exec-reveal">
        <div class="agent-card-header">
          <div class="agent-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1" ry="1"/><path d="M9 14l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="agent-label-text">Queue Agent</div>
            <div class="agent-name">Task Completion &amp; Prioritization</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-desc">Autonomously works operational queues: intake processing, authorization follow-ups, appointment confirmations, referral tracking. Escalates exceptions. Learns from outcomes to improve over time.</div>
        <div class="agent-impact">
          <div class="agent-impact-label">Why Your CEO Cares</div>
          <div class="agent-impact-text">The work that required <strong>15 coordinators</strong> now requires <strong>5 plus agents</strong>. Headcount stays flat while patient volume grows. Your board sees a cost structure that your competitors cannot match.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Profile Agent -->
      <div class="agent-card exec-reveal">
        <div class="agent-card-header">
          <div class="agent-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="agent-label-text">Profile Agent</div>
            <div class="agent-name">Patient Intelligence</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-desc">Maintains living patient profiles that auto-update from every interaction. Surfaces care gaps, flags anomalies, and ensures no profile goes stale between visits. Feeds data upstream to clinical and compliance modules.</div>
        <div class="agent-impact">
          <div class="agent-impact-label">Why Your Board Cares</div>
          <div class="agent-impact-text">Care gap detection shifts from <strong>quarterly audit findings</strong> to <strong>real-time alerts</strong>. Compliance risk drops. Patient outcomes improve. The board gets a dashboard, not a surprise.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Revenue Agent -->
      <div class="agent-card exec-reveal">
        <div class="agent-card-header">
          <div class="agent-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="agent-label-text">Revenue Agent</div>
            <div class="agent-name">Appropriate Coding (ACD)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-desc">Codes encounters in real time using the ACD module. Catches undercoding before it becomes revenue left on the table. Ensures every interaction is documented correctly for payer submission.</div>
        <div class="agent-impact">
          <div class="agent-impact-label">Why Your CFO Cares</div>
          <div class="agent-impact-text">Revenue capture improves by <strong>12–18%</strong> in the first quarter. Coding accuracy goes from a rearview mirror metric to a real-time guarantee. Denied claims from documentation errors approach <strong>zero</strong>.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .exec-agentic {
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 120px 40px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .agentic-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .agentic-bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .agentic-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.82);
  }

  .agentic-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .agent-intro-text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 740px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .agent-intro-text strong {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .agent-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .agent-card {
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, var(--navy-mid), var(--navy-light));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .agent-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: rgba(240,180,41,0.2);
  }

  .agent-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--teal));
    border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
  }

  .agent-card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .agent-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(240,180,41,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .agent-label-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .agent-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .agent-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .agent-impact {
    background: rgba(240,180,41,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(240,180,41,0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
  }

  .agent-impact-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .agent-impact-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-100);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .agent-impact-text strong {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .agent-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .exec-agentic {
      padding: 80px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
